| Alignment guard | `_check_alignment` raises `ValueError` on length mismatch |
| Confederation + None ranking | `resolve_ranking` falls back to static map |
| Deterministic | no stochastic elements; `random_seed` stored for future use |
| No forward leakage | state read before row, updated after |

